tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ai_bias_data (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    audit_log TEXT,
    monitoring_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE audit_logs (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  event_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE monitoring_data (
  data_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  model_id UUID,
  accuracy FLOAT,
  bias_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE audit_logs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action VARCHAR(255),
    details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE monitoring_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    accuracy FLOAT,
    false_positives INT,
    false_negatives INT
);

CREATE TABLE bias_analysis (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    bias_score FLOAT,
    impact TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action VARCHAR(255),
    details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE monitoring_data (
    data_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    algorithm_id INT NOT NULL,
    performance_metric VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    bias_level DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE bias_analysis (
    analysis_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT NOT NULL,
    dataset_id INT NOT NULL,
    bias_detected BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    bias_type VARCHAR(50)
);
